lead_paragraph: England's newspapers reacted with outrage to the country's 2-1 defeat to Iceland at Euro 2016, condemning the performance as "clueless" and "confused" and pouring scorn on departed manager Roy Hodgson.

headline.print_headline: British Media Decry 'Clueless' England After Loss to Iceland
